snippet: An article on Saturday about the popularity of abalone on the Northern California coast misspelled the surname of a landscape architect who lives in the Sea Ranch, near Stewarts Point. He is Lawrence Halprin, not Halpern....
lead_paragraph: An article on Saturday about the popularity of abalone on the Northern California coast misspelled the surname of a landscape architect who lives in the Sea Ranch, near Stewarts Point. He is Lawrence Halprin, not Halpern.
